                <note rend="inline" type="source">422.11G93/1028: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Ecuador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hartman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-09T12:00:00-05:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1919, noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received May 10, 3.20 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister of Finance informed me today that Ecuadorean Government remitted draft
                    yesterday to London 10,500 pounds sterling account service Guayaquil and Quito
                    Railway bonds.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
